title: UFOs Over Chicago - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 10/15/21

description:
Guest host Ian Punnett and Illinois UFO investigators Sam Maranto and TJ Japcon explore recordings and mass UFO sightings around the Chicago area, as well as interviewing Ian's own wife and son about a glowing UFO they saw themselves last month in Chicago.
